{"lemma":"طَلَبَةُ","slug":"طَلَبَةُ","root":"ط.ل.ب","root_slug":"ط-ل-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ل-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طالِب","root":"طلب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26892","n26899","n26900","n26901"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"seeker, pursuer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"student","examples":[{"text":"وبهذا المسجد جماعة من الطلبة يتعلمون العلم ولهم مرتبات من مال المسجد، وله مطبخة يصنع فيها الطعام للوارد والصادر ولإطعام الفقراء من المسلمين بها.","english":"In this mosque also there are a number of students of religious science who receive stipends from its revenue, and it has a kitchen from which all travellers and the poor Muslims of the town are supplied with food."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"scholar"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"claimant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"applicant, petitioner"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"candidate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to request, to demand, to ask for"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of طَلَبَ (ṭalaba)."},"ipa":["/tˤaː.lib/","/tˤaː.la.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26892","headword_ar":"طَلَبَهُ","root":"Tlb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalabN","text_ar":"طَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, MA, O, Msb, K &c.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTolabN","text_ar":"مَطْلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, MA, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilaAbN","text_ar":"طِلَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilaAbapN","text_ar":"طِلَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, MA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibapN","text_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTolaAbN","text_ar":"تَطْلَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is of a measure denoting intensiveness]; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiT~alabahu","text_ar":"اِطَّلَبَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, O, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTl~bhu","text_ar":"تطلّبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) [but see this last below;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought it, desired it, demanded it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asked for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pursued it, pursued after it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prosecuted it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought, desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavoured, to find it and to get"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba","text_ar":"طَلَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also expl. as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AtbE","text_ar":"اتبع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atobaEa","text_ar":"اَتْبَعَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he followed in pursuit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AuTolubo liY $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"اُطْلُبْ لِى شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seek thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for me, a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabahu minohu","text_ar":"طَلَبَهُ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought it, desired it, demanded it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asked for it, of him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba A_ilaY~a","text_ar":"طَلَبَ اـِلَىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragiba","text_ar":"رَغِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He petitioned me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made petition to me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba A_ilayohi","text_ar":"طَلَبَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saA^alahu","text_ar":"سَاَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he asked him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or [it means]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabahu raAgibFA A_ilayohi","text_ar":"طَلَبَهُ رَاغِبًا اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought him, petitioning him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; for it is generally held that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba","text_ar":"طَلَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not trans. by means of a prep., therefore they explain the like of this phrase as implicative. (MF, TA.) See also 4, in two places: and see 5. You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabahu biHaq~K","text_ar":"طَلَبَهُ بِحَقٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAlabahu","text_ar":"طَالَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba bivaA^orihi","text_ar":"طَلَبَ بِثَاْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi*aHolihi","text_ar":"بِذَحْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought to obtain his blood-revenge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaliation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba bidamihi","text_ar":"طَلَبَ بِدَمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S and Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Hl","text_ar":"ذحل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~iraAju yaTolubu","text_ar":"السِّرَاجُ يَطْلُبُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yanoTafiy^a","text_ar":"اَنْ يَنْطَفِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lamp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lighted wick, is near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"about, to become extinguished"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jidaArN yuriydu A^ano yanoqaD~a","text_ar":"جِدَارٌ يُرِيدُ اَنْ يَنْقَضَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taliba","text_ar":"طَلِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalabN","text_ar":"طَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[accord. to the TK said of a man,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, distant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remote."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. [See also 4.])"}],"source_refs":["Msb","A","MA","K","TA","O","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n26899","headword_ar":"طُلْبَةٌ","root":"Tlb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A far-extending journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safarN TaluwbN","text_ar":"سَفَرٌ طَلُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26900","headword_ar":"طِلْبَةٌ","root":"Tlb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of seeking"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: an inf. n. of modality, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilosapN","text_ar":"جِلْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. ―         -b2-  And] a subst from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAlabahu","text_ar":"طَالَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibapN","text_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u Tilobapa","text_ar":"اُمُّ طِلْبَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eagle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n26901","headword_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ","root":"Tlb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talabahu","text_ar":"طَلَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (MA.) ―         -b2-  [It generally signifies]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that one seeks, desires, demands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asks for; a thing that one seeks, desires,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours, to find and to get"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take; an object of quest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desire;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilaAbN","text_ar":"طِلَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is originally an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAlabahu","text_ar":"طَالَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilobN","text_ar":"طِلْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Har p. 560;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilobapN","text_ar":"طِلْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalabN","text_ar":"طَلَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAlabahu","text_ar":"طَالَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) signifying [the same, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demanded:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibapN","text_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need; a needful thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibaAtN","text_ar":"طَلِبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY Einodahu","text_ar":"لِى عِنْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilobapN","text_ar":"طِلْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibapN","text_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have an object of quest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, necessary to be sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demanded, of him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa Tilobu","text_ar":"هِىَ طِلْبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She is the object of love of such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tilobatuhu","text_ar":"طِلْبَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, K:) or the former, (O,) or each, the latter mentioned by Lh, (TA,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she is the object of quest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the object of love, of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.)       -A2-  And it is said on the authority of IAar that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tlbp","text_ar":"طلبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app., accord. to the context,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalibapN","text_ar":"طَلِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assembly, of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TK","TA","A","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}